<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fēng ér juǎn lián lí míng dào 迦南342</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fēng ér juǎn lián, lí míng dào, xiǎo yǔ shuā shuā kòu mén chuāng,
 yé sū cí shēng huàn nǐ xǐng wǒ men xiāng jù shèng shān shàng,
 lā qǐ shǒu shì xīn zhǎng chéng, shǐ mìng chén zhòng zài jiān shàng
 zài kǔ zài nán zūn zhǔ zhǐ, fú yīn zǎo rì chuán wàn bāng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>342</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>